data.description: This single (family) home is CUTE and ready to mingle! A brick ranch in Botetourt County on a quiet lot with a fenced flat back yard and mountain views may be exactly what you've been looking for! The modernized kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances and newly added and updated cabinetry. Pretty hardwood flooring, two fireplaces, 2.5 bathrooms.  Septic pumped and HVAC serviced in 2020. The front yard has a gentle slope and the side yard goes all the way to the second split-rail fence, so it seems huge! Basement is ready for any flooring of your choice. Very convenient to the new Colonial Elementary, Food Lion, Rainbow Forest Lake, and Rainbow Forest Baptist Church. Call your wingman realtor today and get ready to make this your home sweet home.
